snippet.title: Cat Simulator 2 Cinematic Trailer iOS Android
snippet.description:
Experience life as an actual cat, embark on adventures through expansive residences and breathtaking gardens. Select from a variety of cats and personalize their appearance to your liking. Test your skills in time-based challenges and, of course, revel in annoying humans. Engage in playful interactions with fellow kittens through the exciting new multiplayer mode, inviting friends or competing against individuals from across the globe!

Android
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.swiftappskom.catsimulator2

iOS
https://apps.apple.com/au/app/cat-simulator-2/id1667335436
